      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1049 - It was narrated from Humran ibn A'yan, from one of the Imams (as), who said:\n\"My father (as) when he prayed while sitting, he would sit cross-legged, and when he went into ruku' (bowing), he would fold his legs.\""
